1. Ja sam prepoznao* tvoj glas odmah. (I recognized your voice immediately.)
2. Ona nije prepoznala* svog bivšeg dečka na ulici. (She didn't recognize her ex-boyfriend on the street.)
3. Da li ćeš ikada prepoznati* svoju grešku? (Will you ever recognize your mistake?)
4. Kada sam ga prepoznao*, pozvao sam ga da se pridruži našoj grupi. (When I recognized him, I invited him to join our group.)
5. Ona je odmah prepoznala* svoju torbu među ostalim torbama na aerodromu. (She immediately recognized her bag among the other bags at the airport.)
6. Policija je prepoznala* pljačkaša na snimku nadzorne kamere. (The police recognized the robber on the surveillance camera footage.)
7. Zbog svoje brzine i spretnosti, on je prepoznat* kao jedan od najboljih igrača u timu. (Due to his speed and agility, he is recognized as one of the best players on the team.)
8. Prepoznavanje* lica postalo je vrlo važno za sigurnost u društvu. (Facial recognition has become very important for security in society.)
9. Ona je vrlo dobra u prepoznavanju* emocija na licima drugih ljudi. (She is very good at recognizing emotions on other people's faces.)
10. Nakon što je pročitao knjigu, prepoznao* je neke od glavnih tema u njoj. (After reading the book, he recognized some of the main themes in it.)